{"tid":1603551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日見到好多新手裝都行得好前，我向你地致敬但同時希望各位留意","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:23:55.000Z","uid":247905,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9ab978d981ae05922c00db1095deead2e3ca84","tid":1603551,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">相信好多和班非都升級左做勇武，但勇武除左心態，裝備都好重要，一個都不能少唔係淨係用口講，係要實行，你要保護到自己先有能力保護到其他人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">首先見到好多師兄得個3M眼罩，我想講基本上係無用，因為唔密封<br />\n解決方法可以入面加泳鏡，或者學下面教學改裝</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［眼罩心得］買唔到密封眼罩既入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1407078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1407078</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">另外眼罩無反光貼其實好易俾人認到，你保障緊自己同時亦係保障緊其他手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n夢遊嘅眼罩要貼反光貼啊，特別係用6800嘅手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[721 - 裝備] 眼罩都係時候要進化！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">仲有好多得個6006無棉就上前，其實唔係好頂得<br />\n附上說明等你了解自己防具去到咩level</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3M半面豬嘴全攻略 濾罐 濾棉 棉蓋說明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491913</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">防具詳細教學post</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【油漆教學】成日話豬咀冇用 因為你地買漏／錯野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n728後最新解答疑問 [推到全人類有豬嘴] 百幾蚊就100%防!!!! 豬嘴護目鏡攻略(應對對方升級催淚彈)!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">新手上前行行企企唔知做咩好？<br />\n可以試下由簡單消防入手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[香城online攻略] 滅火攻略update<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">到今日都仲見到前線有人係探病look<br />\n要改善喇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[721見] 如何正確隱藏身份 (整合+進階篇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327279</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">最後，希望大家心態上都可以終極進化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n10.1大戰 但你地心態準備好未先？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602613</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">10.1見<br />\n不分和勇 齊上齊落<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ed6c15b340e72f1221adea8f660cdb90f76eaaa5","tid":1603551,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6080c68f1ba0f006fdb4989d45a6f7b547209d","tid":1603551,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoFPyJu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoFPyJu.jpg&h=15c1aa64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d851b2fe0052672df8e353aa69c24586b885966f","tid":1603551,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:09:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"548131b21023535bfce3f007a07b44d534ab07de","tid":1603551,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:10:08.000Z","msg":"前線要既唔係索帶, 唔係士巴拿, 唔係較剪<br />\n- 